-- Shell Plans to Investigate Leak on Oil Pipeline in Nigeria
-- B y   E l i s h a   B a l a - G b o g b o
-- 2012-09-04T09:46:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-04/shell-plans-to-investigate-leak-on-oil-pipeline-in-nigeria.html
Royal Dutch Shell Plc said it plans
to investigate the cause of a leak that closed the pipeline
leading to the Nembe Creek-2 flowstation in Nigeria.  “A joint investigation visit is planned to determine the
cause of the leak, preparatory to repairs,”  Precious Okolobo , a
spokesman, said by phone today from Lagos, the commercial
capital.  To contact the reporter on this story:
